<summary>
The <strong><c>text-align</c></strong> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</see> property sets the horizontal alignment of the inline-level content inside a block element or table-cell box. This means it works like <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/vertical-align">vertical-align</see> but in the horizontal direction.
</summary>
